==English==
===Noun===
'''Ayyavazhi'''
{{wikipedia}}
# A [[religion]], originated in South India in the Mid-nintheenth Century. According to it's source, [[Akilattirattu Ammanai]], [[Ayya Vaikundar]] was the incarnation of [[Ekam]]. 

